title: I didnt get my mistery skin or icon for 10 years of riot
body: I have Riot Kayle but i didnt get a mistery skin or 10 year icon. Plz help and sry for bad english

replies.body: It looks like Okuma provided some solid insight, but I wanted to to reiterate that gifts are still being sent out, and you may not get every item all at once.  You can also stay updated at our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until this is all wrapped up!

> Hey guys! Those of you who haven't yet received their gift, worry not! Our initial deadline has passed however the gifting is continuing and taking longer than expected. Our new ETA on finishing is end of day 30th of September - so please allow until after this date before submitting tickets! Sorry for the delays!


Direct quote from Riot Eambo
